  "session_notes": "Fasted training (6am, eating window starts at noon).\n**Held back intentionally.** Could have pushed more but consciously didn't. No specific recovery flag — self-regulated effort.\n**Machine squat regressed −3 kg** (53 → 50). Two sessions now off the 4/20 baseline. Reclaim 53 next leg day.\n**Calves flat 5 sessions running.** 4/20 flag (bump to 45 kg) unactioned across three leg days. Push 45 kg × 15 × 3 next session — non-negotiable.\n**Leg press held at 120 × 15 × 3.** Second session at the regressed rep target — didn't reclaim 4/20 AMRAP (20/20/20).\n**Seated leg curl held at 25 kg.** Still −3 kg below 4/20 baseline. Push 28 next session.\nJacob skipped leg press (lower back pain). Loads on deadlift, squat, and leg curl all held same as 4/23.\nPer [[project_pt_programming_style|PT programming pattern]]: heavy compound first (deadlift), so leg curl + calf numbers are post-fatigue — don't read as fresh capacity.",
